{"word":"μεταλλάω","slug":"μεταλλάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n66763\" key=\"metalla/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μεταλλ-άω</orth>, <sense id=\"n66763.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">search carefully, inquire diligently</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐμοὶ οὐ φίλον ἐστὶ μεταλλῆσαι καὶ ἐρέσθαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:378\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.378</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐκέτι μέμνηται . . , οὐδὲ μεταλλᾷ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:15:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.23</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n66763.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. acc. pers., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">inquire of, question</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σε . . οὔτ᾽ εἴρομαι οὔτε μεταλλῶ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:553\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.553</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:69\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.69</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:16:287\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.287</biblScope> </bibl>; but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντεφθέγξατο . . μετάλλασέν τέ νιν</foreign> the voice <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sought</tr_> him <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">out</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:62\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">O.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.62</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n66763.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. acc. objecti, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">inquire about, ask after</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μή τι σὺ ταῦτα διείρεο μηδὲ μετάλλα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:550\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.550</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:516\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.516</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἕταροι δὲ κατέκταθεν, οὓς σὺ μεταλλᾷς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:780\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.780</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:125\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.125</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:19:190\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.190</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἕκαστα μ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:128\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.128</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greek